            <li class="list-group-item d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
                <span>Income Documents for <strong>ID: 23101B0008</strong> approved</span>
                <span class="badge bg-primary rounded-pill">Approved</span>
            </li>
            <li class="list-group-item d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
